    "body": "Can you describe your ideal UX? \r\n\r\nAs a workaround ,your test contract can inherit the contract being tested, \r\n\r\ne.g.\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\ncontract Foo {\r\n       function foo() internal { ... }\r\n}\r\ncontract FooTest is Test, Foo {\r\n       function testFoo() {\r\n            require(foo() == ..., \"error\");\r\n       }\r\n}\r\n```",
